  "text": "Paired authors reviewed the titles of the citations identified in the electronic search for relevance to active surveillance. If any single author thought it to be potentially relevant, it was retrieved for further review. We did not seek to identify every article that described a given active surveillance system-a single article that alerted us to the presence of the system was sufficient. We created a working definition for the purposes of the scanning exercise. For our review, an active surveillance system has the following features (the first four were adapted from the work by Aronson and colleagues) [CITATION_1] :",
